Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我來自萊澤塔尼亞名叫芙羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請大家多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你來就來好歹事先通知我一聲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為陛下送我鳳凰星武祭的門票的條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要絕對向公主殿下保密嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他還是那麼愛胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你穿成這樣肯定也是皇兄教你的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的陛下說穿成這樣過去公主殿下一眼就能認出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真受不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過這和我平常的服裝差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}女僕裝嗎為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉是一名在王宮內工作的侍女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛現在還只能算是見習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過真是令人吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒想到裏斯妃特前輩奮鬥的原因竟然是為了孤兒院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其 其實沒那麼誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了那個芙羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲在故鄉時是一個什麼樣的人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼突然問這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是就是單純有點好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你問是個什麼樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我覺得和現在沒什麼差別哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}和我們在一起的時候非常溫柔讓人覺得很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而在城堡裏時則英姿颯爽非常地帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以和現在沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼請大家看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這些是大家和公主殿下的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為有修女提出想盡可能用實際形式把回憶留存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}受她的影響孩子們也開始經常拍照了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那是公主殿下幫芙羅拉洗頭時的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你看了嗎?看到了嗎?看到了對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒 沒有沒看到沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉我不是跟你說過好多遍要刪掉那張照片的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是可是這是我和公主殿下難得的寶貴回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看來芙羅拉你非常喜歡尤莉絲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的公主殿下是芙羅拉非常崇拜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉打算將來也要以學生的身份來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後像公主殿下那樣幫助孤兒院的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我不是跟你說過沒必要那麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是可是芙羅拉也想幫助大家呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你現在還小不用在意那種事可以再
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可我聽說界龍學生會長的年紀比芙羅拉還要小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼芙羅拉應該也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你至少還要個兩年才能達到入學年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}到那個時候我已經將你的願望全部達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之前分別的時候我應該也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我一定會幫助你們改變那個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為此我會稱霸所有的星武祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道你對我這麼沒信心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不愧是裏斯妃特連目標也這麼遠大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是事情不會像你想的那麼順利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}至少這次的鳳凰星武祭冠軍是屬於我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對吧綺凜?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我 我也不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為我有絕不能退讓的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沙沙宮小姐和刀藤小姐是公主殿下他們的競爭對手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}競爭對手!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好像確實是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}呃夜吹他還沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}比如說關於你姐姐的事這個如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽說他以前好像見過使用這把純星煌式武裝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}晚上好普莉熙拉同學抱歉突然聯絡你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不會沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其實我一直想著必須向天霧同學道謝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但因為現在是星武祭舉行期間擔心可能會打擾到你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}前段時間的事情真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不會我並沒有做什麼值得你道謝的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧同學幫我把姐姐帶了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這一點真是讓我感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了我可以再邀請天霧同學來吃一頓晚餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好啦換我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喲天霧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}晚上好依蕾奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}反正你要找的肯定不是普莉熙拉而是我吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不這麼說也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其實你真正要找的人也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而是狄路克那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你猜得真準
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}遺憾的是我這是照搬狄路克那混蛋的話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他說你近期內很有可能為了接觸他而主動發來聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那你能幫我轉告他一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就說我有一些關千天霧遙的問題想問他希望和他見個面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可以反正這也是我分內的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那多謝啦幫我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過你可要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他手底下的爪牙可不僅僅只有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}據說連那個「孤毒魔女」都是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「孤毒魔女」?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且他手下還有黑貓機關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}黑貓機關?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是雷渥夫的諜報機關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那群人真的很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要是命令再骯髒的活她們都照辦不誤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知道了我會提高警覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知道就好性命才是根本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了對了今天的比賽我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們好像打得很辛苦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}托你的福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是大快人心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧同學不好意思能不能請你等一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要好好向他道個謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不是 那個 怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是覺得我也姑且應該跟你道個謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是姑且而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}道謝?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是那個啦「霸潰血鐮」的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然不太想承認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且你弄壞了它也害得我不好賺錢過得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這一點似乎也是事實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼啊原來是那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你救了我多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}接下來就看惡辣之王會怎麼行動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀真是好久沒回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}夜吹?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉吵醒你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒關係啦說起來我們好久沒見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為星武祭期間可是賺錢的大好時機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}說起來昨天的比賽我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}首先恭喜你晉級四分之一決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是一場險勝就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好啦好啦反正贏了這就足夠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後下一場的對手是界龍那對雙胞胎對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那兩個傢伙很難對付哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且個性更是惡劣到了極點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我看過比賽資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}感覺他們確實相當擅長針對對手的弱點來攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為他們真的很擅長髮揮星僊術的優點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對上他們不管是誰都會覺得無比難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}星僊術的優點?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了你這是頭一回對上道士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}星僊術就是將「魔女」或「魔術師」的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}歸結為一種技術並泛用化的招式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「魔女」和「魔術師」大多會使用比較突出的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但相對的會缺乏穩定性並且容易被找出反製法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是道士就沒有這一類的弱點了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是這樣啊謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}太好了你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嗯怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}其實...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉說想找你一起吃午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好像有些事無論如何都想要問問你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然前提是你不嫌棄的話
