Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼? 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之後我會告訴你的尤莉絲你們先在這裏等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等一下我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們是搭檔吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可.. 可是會長只找天霧同學一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒關繫帶他們過來可羅奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}機會難得我也順便和「華焰魔女」見上一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉芙羅拉我們臨時有事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你能一個人回旅館吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你小子就是「叢雲」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}一臉呆樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣的人竟然能排序列第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}星導館也沒什麼大不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}也不知道是誰為了擊潰這個呆呆的傢伙而特地派人過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}惡辣之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}完全不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}虧你能這麼厚顏無恥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}前幾天依蕾奈· 兀兒塞絲親口說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是你要把綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}依蕾奈也只是當時偷偷告訴我們罷了我們沒有任何證據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而且繼續追究的話會給她帶來麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的腦子倒還算靈光嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為我想問的事情和那個無關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過在你開口之前我先提醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我沒有義務回答你的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}給我記好這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但如果是這樣的話你又為何特地來這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是一時興起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}無比忙碌的學生會長竟然因為一時興起跑來這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼可能是因為我這裏也有能夠提供給你的東西沒錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要想得到什麼東西就得付出一些其它的東西來換取
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不然交易就無法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好吧你合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你想問什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}關於我姐姐 天霧遙 告訴我你知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}很遺憾我知道的也不多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}僅僅見過她一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}蝕武祭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你知道這個嗎尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那是一群看膩了星武祭的垃圾們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為了追求更猛烈的刺激而創造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}非法,不講規則的戰鬥遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不講規則
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}孰勝孰負要看哪一方選手先昏厥 或是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}失去性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽說有一部分有錢人是這種比賽的狂熱擁躉一度還挺火爆的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過那個已經
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒錯在很久之前就被剷除消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為警備隊長大人看它不順眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我曾經看到天霧遙作為出場選手之一參加了那個比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你說姐姐她參加了那個比賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為她當時使用的是「黑爐魔劍」所以我印象很深
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼那場比賽結果如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧遙輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}喂綾鬥你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過她好像沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}至千她之後的情況我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我就見過天霧遙這麼一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼接下來換我提問了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}小子你和瑪狄阿思· 梅薩是什麼關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}瑪狄阿思· 梅薩 你說的是星武祭的運營委員長?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看你的樣子好像並不是在故意裝傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}話都說完了趕緊滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我還有一個疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你究竟是怎麼知道我們所在的地方的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們是在幾小時前才剛剛定下去那家店的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要是我們事先有過預約記錄那還說得通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但在這麼短時間裏你究竟是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}蠢貨我沒有義務回答你這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}之前我去接天霧同學和裏斯妃特同學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看到有一個很可愛的女孩和他們在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}感覺就像洋娃娃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她究竟是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}會長給我的資料上也沒有記載
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過她年紀還很小身上也沒佩戴校徽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以我覺得她肯定不是「六芒星」的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對了對了那個女孩還穿著女僕裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}女僕哦女僕
